  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our games you might like</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096510/extras/71a304bdd314c1f22be8981e78e80ff8.avif?t=1757886239\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><br><strong>The leaders of the seven nations failed to reach a peace agreement. All kingdoms are now at war.</strong><br><br>Seven Nations is a real-time battle game. Seven villages develop in real time and then send their units to wage war on the neighbouring villages.<br>You can decide to control the construction of your village yourself or let an AI do it. You can also control the time and many other parameters!<br><br><strong><i>Which nation will win?</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1096510/extras/fa49507954fb1d519a559094d42da0f1.webp?t=1757886239\" width=600 height=38 /></span><br><br><strong>Features :</strong><br><br>■ More than 8 different types of buildings!<br>■ A large number of parameters that can be modified!<br>■ Day / Night Cycle!<br>■ Many different units!<br>■ Nice background music!<br>■ Real-time warfare! ( RTS)",
